                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "effect": "You destroy the staff, unleashing a blast of arcane power in a 30- foot cone, dealing 2d6 force damage per charge remaining in the staff with a DC 30 basic Reflex save.",
                    "traits": [
                        {
                            "name": "Death",
